<p class="main">
				Welcome to Magellanic Games' website.  <b class="redText">Liam Charalambous (a.k.a Magellanic)</b> is a software developer from southern England. Currently he is working on (amongst other projects) his first game: <b class="redText">Mr.Blocked</b> with musician, artist and general tech enthusiast <a class="pinkText" href="https://www.protodome.com">PROTODOME</a>.
        You can view projects both here and on <a class="pinkText" href="https://github.com/MagellanicGames">Github</a>.
</p>

